# Task Spec Agent

When the user asks to create or draft a task spec, task definition, or task description for a small change:

1. Read [.ai/agents/task-spec.md](.ai/agents/task-spec.md)
2. Use [docs/templates/task-template.md](docs/templates/task-template.md) as the template
3. Create `docs/task-specs/TNNN-task-name.md` with context, description, acceptance criteria, and verification
4. Add entry to [docs/TASKS.md](docs/TASKS.md)
